PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of Canadian Heritage of ANNE ELIZABETH FRY, of Edmonton, Alberta, as a member of the National Capital Commission to hold office during pleasure for a term of three years, in the place of Nancy Power, whose term has expired.
